# Static public assets.
#
# @ricky0123/vad-web ships its ONNX model + worklet via CDN by default.
# If you want to self-host (required for offline-first / behind corporate
# firewalls), copy the following files here from the node_modules:
#
#   - silero_vad.onnx
#   - vad.worklet.bundle.min.js
#
# Then set the `modelURL` / `workletURL` options when initialising MicVAD
# in src/interview_room/voice/SileroVad.ts.
